On 10/22/03 8:30 AM, "Jay Brown" <jayb(-at-)coedsportswear.com> wrote:

> I need to get a new engine hatch for a '79 I am selling for a friend.  Since
> there is no hatch present I am going to have to visit the local pick-n-pull
> to get one.  What other year engine hatches will fit on a '79 without
> modification?  It appears that the same seal fits all from '71-'79, but I
> seem to recall that there are differences in hinge size and position and
> possibly the latch as well...

You want a 77-79 lid because that's when the hinges changed.

The seal is compatible from 72-79.

